              <li><strong>Regular APR:</strong> 19.24% - 29.24% Variable</li>
              <li><strong>Foreign Trans. Fee:</strong> 3%</li>
              <li><strong>Credit Required:</strong> Good/Excellent</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="meta-info">
            <p>Earn 1% when you buy and 1% as you pay for those purchases. Ideal for simplicity. Application Tip: Ensure your credit score is at least 670 before applying.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Cash Back: Chase Freedom -->
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-header">
            <div>
              <h3>Chase Freedom</h3>
              <span class="category-badge">Best for Everyday Spending</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="features-list">
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Rewards Rate:</strong> 1.5% - 5%</li>
              <li><strong>Annual Fee:</strong> $0</li>
              <li><strong>Sign-up Bonus:</strong> Yes</li>
              <li><strong>Regular APR:</strong> 20.49% - 29.24% Variable</li>
              <li><strong>Foreign Trans. Fee:</strong> 3%</li>
              <li><strong>Credit Required:</strong> Good/Excellent</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="meta-info">
            <p>Earn 3% on dining and drugstores, and 1.5% on everything else. Pairs well with premium Chase cards.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Travel: Chase Sapphire -->
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-header">
            <div>
              <h3>Chase Sapphire</h3>
              <span class="category-badge">Best Entry-Level Travel</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="features-list">
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Rewards Rate:</strong> 2x - 5x points</li>
              <li><strong>Annual Fee:</strong> $95</li>
              <li><strong>Sign-up Bonus:</strong> 60,000 pts</li>
              <li><strong>Regular APR:</strong> 21.49% - 28.49% Variable</li>
              <li><strong>Foreign Trans. Fee:</strong> None</li>
              <li><strong>Credit Required:</strong> Good/Excellent</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="meta-info">
            <p>Points are worth 25% more when redeemed for travel through Chase. Excellent travel protections included.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Travel: Amex Gold/Platinum -->
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-header">
            <div>
              <h3>Amex Gold / Platinum</h3>
              <span class="category-badge">Best Premium Travel Perks</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="features-list">
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Rewards Rate:</strong> 1x - 5x points</li>
              <li><strong>Annual Fee:</strong> $250 - $695</li>
              <li><strong>Sign-up Bonus:</strong> High</li>
              <li><strong>Regular APR:</strong> See Terms</li>
              <li><strong>Foreign Trans. Fee:</strong> None</li>
              <li><strong>Credit Required:</strong> Good/Excellent</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="meta-info">
            <p>High fees offset by massive lifestyle credits, Uber cash, dining credits, and lounge access (Platinum).</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Travel: Capital One Venture -->
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-header">
            <div>
              <h3>Capital One Venture</h3>
              <span class="category-badge">Best Flat-Rate Travel</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="features-list">
