              <li><strong>Rewards Rate:</strong> 2x miles</li>
              <li><strong>Annual Fee:</strong> $95</li>
              <li><strong>Sign-up Bonus:</strong> 75,000 miles</li>
              <li><strong>Regular APR:</strong> 19.99% - 29.99% Variable</li>
              <li><strong>Foreign Trans. Fee:</strong> None</li>
              <li><strong>Credit Required:</strong> Good/Excellent</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="meta-info">
            <p>Earn 2x miles on every purchase, every day. Includes up to $100 credit for Global Entry or TSA PreCheck.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- No Annual Fee -->
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-header">
            <div>
              <h3>Top No Annual Fee Card</h3>
              <span class="category-badge">Best No Annual Fee</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="features-list">
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Rewards Rate:</strong> Varies</li>
              <li><strong>Annual Fee:</strong> $0</li>
              <li><strong>Sign-up Bonus:</strong> Varies</li>
              <li><strong>Regular APR:</strong> Varies</li>
              <li><strong>Foreign Trans. Fee:</strong> Varies</li>
              <li><strong>Credit Required:</strong> Good</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="meta-info">
            <p>A great option for those who want to earn rewards without paying a yearly fee.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Balance Transfer (0% APR) -->
        <div class="card">
