            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="features-list">
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Rewards Rate:</strong> None</li>
              <li><strong>Annual Fee:</strong> Varies</li>
              <li><strong>Sign-up Bonus:</strong> None</li>
              <li><strong>Intro APR:</strong> 0% for up to 21 months</li>
              <li><strong>Foreign Trans. Fee:</strong> Varies</li>
              <li><strong>Credit Required:</strong> Good/Excellent</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="meta-info">
            <p>Excellent for paying off existing debt with a long 0% promotional APR period.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Business -->
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-header">
            <div>
              <h3>Top Business Card</h3>
              <span class="category-badge">Best for Business</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="features-list">
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Rewards Rate:</strong> Varies</li>
              <li><strong>Annual Fee:</strong> Varies</li>
              <li><strong>Sign-up Bonus:</strong> Varies</li>
              <li><strong>Regular APR:</strong> Varies</li>
              <li><strong>Foreign Trans. Fee:</strong> Varies</li>
              <li><strong>Credit Required:</strong> Excellent</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="meta-info">
            <p>Ideal for small business owners looking to maximize rewards on business expenses.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Student -->
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-header">
            <div>
              <h3>Top Student Card</h3>
              <span class="category-badge">Best for Students</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="features-list">
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Rewards Rate:</strong> Varies</li>
              <li><strong>Annual Fee:</strong> $0</li>
              <li><strong>Sign-up Bonus:</strong> Varies</li>
              <li><strong>Regular APR:</strong> Varies</li>
              <li><strong>Foreign Trans. Fee:</strong> None</li>
              <li><strong>Credit Required:</strong> No History Needed</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="meta-info">
            <p>Build credit while earning rewards. Often designed for those with no credit history.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Building Credit -->
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-header">
            <div>
              <h3>Top Secured Card</h3>
              <span class="category-badge">Best for Building Credit</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="features-list">
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Rewards Rate:</strong> None</li>
              <li><strong>Annual Fee:</strong> Varies</li>
              <li><strong>Security Deposit:</strong> Required</li>
              <li><strong>Regular APR:</strong> Varies</li>
              <li><strong>Foreign Trans. Fee:</strong> None</li>
              <li><strong>Credit Required:</strong> Poor/Rebuilding</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="meta-info">
